    <item>
      <title>关西电力因股票出售计划遭遇 50 年来最大跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/kansai-electric-shares-lead-drop-in-sector-on-planned-share-sale</link>
      <description><![CDATA[关西电力公司宣布计划通过出售股票筹集高达 5049 亿日元（32 亿美元）的资金，引发人们对盈利稀释的担忧，此后该公司股价出现至少 50 年来的最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/kansai-electric-shares-lead-drop-in-sector-on-planned-share-sale</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Nov 2024 03:01:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
